    enum WinError

    Overview

    WinError represents Windows' System Error Codes.

    Defined in:

    winerror.cr

    Enum Members

    ERROR_SUCCESS = 0_u32
    ERROR_INVALID_FUNCTION = 1_u32
    ERROR_FILE_NOT_FOUND = 2_u32
